All macros have a Force Quit mapped to -HOME- by default, Functions are all Paused with the tilde key, activate and deactivate each macro with indicated function keys

Golgoroth AFK Script

F5) Hunter AFK Macro
  -Requires you to run Solar Hunter
    -Melee: Proximity Knife 
    -Exotic:  Calibans Hand (Arms, optional)
    -Mod:  Triple Melee Kickstart (Arms)
    -Aspect:  Knock 'Em Down
    -Fragment:  Ember of Torches
    -Fragment:  Ember of Searing
    -Fragment:  Ember of Solace

F8) Titan AFK Macro
  -Requires to run Solar Titan
    -Grenade: Fusion Grenade
    -Exotic:  Ashen Wake (Arms)
    -Mod:  3x Grenade Kickstart (Arm)
    
F9) Warlock AFK Macro
  -Requires you to run Arc Warlock
    -Grenade:  Pulse Grenades
    -Melee: Ball Lightning
    -Exotic:  Fallen Sunstar (Helmet, Prefered)
    -Exotic:  Crown of tempests (Helmet, not as optimal)
    -Mod: 3x Bolstering Detonation (Arms)
    -Mod: 3x Elemental Charge (Legs)
    -Mod: 3x Utility Kickstart (Bond/Class Item)
    -Aspect:  Electrostatic Mind
    -Aspect:  Arc Soul
    -Spark of Ions
    -Spark of Shock
    -Spark of Magnitude
